    content: # PatternFly 5 → PatternFly 6: Comprehensive Migration Checklist

> Compiled from the official PatternFly 6 upgrade guide (https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade/)
> and the full release notes table (https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade/release-notes)

---

## Table of Contents

1. [Prerequisites & Upgrade Process](#1-prerequisites--upgrade-process)
2. [Package / Dependency Changes](#2-package--dependency-changes)
3. [CSS / Token / Variable Changes](#3-css--token--variable-changes)
4. [Class Name Changes](#4-class-name-changes)
5. [Component API Changes (Every Component)](#5-component-api-changes)
6. [Import Path Changes](#6-import-path-changes)
7. [Removed Features & Deprecated Components](#7-removed-features--deprecated-components)
8. [New Required Patterns](#8-new-required-patterns)
9. [Breakpoint Changes](#9-breakpoint-changes)
10. [Test Failure Guidance](#10-test-failure-guidance)
11. [Codemods Reference](#11-codemods-reference)

---

## 1. Prerequisites & Upgrade Process

- [ ] **Complete PF5 upgrade first** — Ensure you're fully on PatternFly 5 before attempting the PF6 migration
- [ ] **Update dependencies** to PF6 versions in `package.json` (not handled by codemods)
- [ ] **Run codemods BEFORE manual changes** (running them after causes more manual work)
- [ ] Run: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6`
- [ ] Review output, then run again with `--fix`
- [ ] Run multiple times until clean
- [ ] Run class-name-updater: `npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <path> --v6 --fix`
- [ ] Run tokens-update codemod for React tokens
- [ ] Run css-vars-updater for .css/.scss/.md files
- [ ] Remove all CSS overrides, then selectively re-add only what's needed
- [ ] Update breakpoint logic from px to rem
- [ ] Run final cleanup: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6 --only data-codemods-cleanup`

---

## 2. Package / Dependency Changes

| Package | Change |
|---------|--------|
| `@patternfly/react-core` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-icons` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-styles` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-tokens` | Major version bump to v6 — token names completely changed |
| `@patternfly/react-charts` | Major version bump; Victory charts moved to subpath `@patternfly/react-charts/victory` |
| `@patternfly/react-table` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-topology` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-component-groups` | Updated with renamed components |
| `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` | New package for drag-and-drop (replaces deprecated DragDrop) |
| `victory` / `victory-core` / `victory-tooltip` | Now **optional peer dependency** — must be installed separately |

---

## 3. CSS / Token / Variable Changes

### 3.1 CSS Variable Prefix Changes

| PF5 Prefix | PF6 Prefix | Notes |
|------------|------------|-------|
| `--pf-v5-global--` | `--pf-t--global--` | New design token system |
| `--pf-v5-c-` | `--pf-v6-c-` | Component variables |
| `--pf-v5-l-` | `--pf-v6-l-` | Layout variables |
| `--pf-v5-u-` | `--pf-v6-u-` | Utility variables |
| `--pf-global--` | `--pf-v6-global--` (or `--pf-t--global--`) | Global variables |

### 3.2 Design Token System

PF6 introduces a **completely new design token system**. The old `--pf-global--*` and `--pf-v5-global--*` variables are replaced with `--pf-t--*` tokens.

**Key token naming changes:**
| PF5 Variable Pattern | PF6 Token Pattern | Example |
|---------------------|-------------------|---------|
| `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` | `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` | Font sizes |
| `--pf-v5-global--spacer--md` | `--pf-t--global--spacer--md` | Spacers |
| `--pf-v5-global--primary-color--100` | `--pf-t--global--color--brand--default` | Colors |
| `--pf-v5-global--BorderWidth--sm` | `--pf-t--global--border--width--regular` | Borders |
| `--pf-v5-global--BoxShadow--sm` | `--pf-t--global--box-shadow--sm` | Shadows |

**React tokens** also completely renamed:
| PF5 React Token | PF6 React Token |
|----------------|-----------------|
| `global_FontSize_lg` | `t_global_font_size_lg` |
| `global_link_Color_hover` | `t_global_color_nonstatus_green_clicked` (example — no 1:1 mapping) |
| `global_primary_color_100` | Mapped to new `t_global_color_*` tokens |

### 3.3 Color Variables

Many color variables have been renamed or reorganized. The `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` token (hot pink) is used by codemods to visually flag variables that need manual replacement.

**Color name changes in props:**
| PF5 Color | PF6 Color |
|-----------|-----------|
| `"cyan"` | `"teal"` |
| `"gold"` | `"yellow"` |

### 3.4 Resources

- [Removed variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [Added variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)
- [All PatternFly tokens](https://www.patternfly.org/tokens/all-patternfly-tokens)

---

## 4. Class Name Changes

### 4.1 Prefix Updates

| PF5 Class Pattern | PF6 Class Pattern |
|-------------------|-------------------|
| `.pf-v5-c-*` | `.pf-v6-c-*` (component classes) |
| `.pf-v5-l-*` | `.pf-v6-l-*` (layout classes) |
| `.pf-v5-u-*` | `.pf-v6-u-*` (utility classes) |
| `.pf-v5-m-*` | `.pf-m-*` (modifier classes — prefix dropped in PF6) |
| `.pf-v5-svg` | `.pf-v6-svg` |

### 4.2 Dark Theme Selectors

| PF5 | PF6 |
|-----|-----|
| `.pf-theme-dark` | `.pf-theme-dark` (unchanged) |
| N/A | `.pf-v6-theme-dark` (new alternative) |

---

## 5. Component API Changes

### Accordion

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `AccordionContent`: `isHidden` prop removed | Visibility now set automatically based on `isExpanded` on AccordionItem | ✅ Yes |
| `AccordionToggle`: `isExpanded` prop moved to `AccordionItem` | Move prop from toggle to item | ✅ Yes |
| `AccordionItem` | Now renders a `div` wrapper element | ❌ No (markup) |

### Alert

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Markup changes | Internal updates | ❌ No |

### Avatar

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `border` prop removed | Replace with `isBordered` prop | ✅ Yes |

### Banner

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `variant` prop removed | Replace with `color` or `status` props | ✅ Yes |
| Color values renamed | `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"` | ✅ Yes |

### Button ⚠️

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Icons must use `icon` prop | No longer pass icons as children; use `icon={<SomeIcon />}` | ✅ Yes (for `variant="plain"` only) |
| `isActive` renamed to `isClicked` | Prop rename | ✅ Yes |
| `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attribute | No longer sets `aria-disabled` on native buttons | ❌ No (behavior) |
| Text wrapper added | `<span class="pf-v6-c-button__text">` wraps button text | ❌ No (markup) |

### Card

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Removed props | `isSelectableRaised`, `isDisabledRaised`, `hasSelectableInput`, `selectableInputAriaLabel`, `onSelectableInputChange`, `isFlat`, `isRounded` | ✅ Yes |
| Clickable card markup updated | `selectableActions.selectableActionId` and `selectableActions.name` no longer needed for clickable-only cards | ✅ Yes |

### Checkbox / Radio

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `isLabelBeforeButton` replaced | Use `labelPosition="start"` instead | ✅ Yes |

### Chip ⚠️ (DEPRECATED)

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Chip deprecated | Moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` | ✅ Yes |
| Replace with Label | `Chip` → `Label variant="outline"`, `ChipGroup` → `LabelGroup` | ✅ Yes |

### Content (formerly Text) ⚠️

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `Text` → `Content` | Component renamed | ✅ Yes |
| `TextContent` → `Content` | Component renamed | ✅ Yes |
| `TextList` → `Content component="ul"` | Replaced with Content + component prop | ✅ Yes |
| `TextListItem` → `Content component="li"` | Replaced with Content + component prop | ✅ Yes |
| `TextProps` → `ContentProps` | Interface renamed | ✅ Yes |
| `TextVariants` → `ContentVariants` | Enum renamed | ✅ Yes |
| `TextListVariants` removed | Use Content component prop directly | ✅ Yes |
| `TextListItemVariants` removed | Use Content component prop directly | ✅ Yes |

**Before:**
```tsx
<TextContent>
  <Text component="h1">Title</Text>
  <Text>Body text</Text>
</TextContent>
```

**After:**
```tsx
<Content>
  <Content component="h1">Title</Content>
  <Content component="p">Body text</Content>
</Content>
```

### DataList

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `DataListAction`: `isPlainButtonAction` removed | No longer needed | ✅ Yes |

### Drawer

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `DrawerHead`: `hasNoPadding` removed | | ✅ Yes |
| `colorVariant` `"light-200"` → `"secondary"` | On DrawerContent, DrawerPanelContent, DrawerSection | ✅ Yes |
| `DrawerColorVariant.light200` → `.secondary` | Enum update | ✅ Yes |
| `DrawerContent`: `"no-background"` variant removed | New `"primary"` value added | ✅ Yes |
| `DrawerPanelBody` no longer rendered inside `DrawerHead` | Use independently | ❌ No (manual) |

### DualListSelector

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Old implementation deprecated | Import from `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` | ✅ Yes |
| Next implementation promoted | Import from `@patternfly/react-core` (was in `/next`) | ✅ Yes |

### Empty State ⚠️

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `EmptyStateHeader` removed | No longer a separate component | ✅ Partially |
| `EmptyStateIcon` removed | No longer a separate component | ✅ Partially |
| Title moved to `titleText` prop on `EmptyState` | Pass title text directly | ✅ Yes |
| Heading level moved to `headingLevel` prop on `EmptyState` | Pass heading level directly | ✅ Yes |
| Icon moved to `icon` prop on `EmptyState` | Pass icon component directly (auto-wrapped by EmptyStateIcon) | ✅ Yes |
| `headerClassName` prop added to `EmptyState` | For styling the header area | ✅ Yes |
| **May require manual updates** | Complex implementations need manual review | ⚠️ Partial |

**Before:**
```tsx
<EmptyState>
  <EmptyStateHeader
    titleText="Empty state"
    headingLevel="h4"
    icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={CubesIcon} />}
  />
  <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>
```

**After:**
```tsx
<EmptyState headingLevel="h4" icon={CubesIcon} titleText="Empty state">
  <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>
```

### ExpandableSection

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `isActive` prop removed | No replacement | ✅ Yes |

### FormGroup ⚠️

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `labelIcon` renamed to `labelHelp` | Use `FormGroupLabelHelp` element for the value | ✅ Yes |
| Markup changed | `labelHelp` element wrapped in `<span className="pf-v6-c-form__group-label-help">` | ❌ No |

### HelperTextItem

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `hasIcon` prop removed | Icon renders automatically when variant ≠ "default" | ✅ Yes |
| `isDynamic` prop removed | No longer needed | ✅ Yes |
| `screenReaderText` behavior changed | Now renders only when variant ≠ "default" | ❌ No |

### JumpLinksItem

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `href` prop now **required** | Was optional | ❌ No |
| `onClick` type updated | `React.MouseEvent` instead of `React.MouseEvent<HTMLAnchorElement>` | ❌ No |

### KebabToggle (REMOVED)

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Replaced with `MenuToggle` | Use `<MenuToggle variant="plain" icon={<EllipsisVIcon />} />` | ✅ Yes |

### Label ⚠️

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `isOverflowLabel` replaced | Use `variant="overflow"` instead | ✅ Yes |
| Color values renamed | `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"` | ✅ Yes |

### LoginMainFooterLinksItem

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Restructured | Now uses Button internally; `linkComponentProps` spread onto Button | ✅ Yes |

### LoginMainHeader

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Markup changed | Uses `div` wrapper instead of `header` element | ❌ No |

### Masthead ⚠️

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `MastheadBrand` renamed to `MastheadLogo` | Old component name now used for new wrapper | ✅ Yes |
| New `MastheadBrand` wraps `MastheadLogo` | Structure change | ✅ Yes |
| `backgroundColor` prop removed | Theming no longer handled React-side | ✅ Yes |
| Structure updated | `MastheadToggle` and `MastheadBrand` should be inside `MastheadMain` | ✅ Yes |

### MenuItemAction

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Markup updated | Uses Button internally; wrapper around action button | ❌ No |

### MenuToggle

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Icons should use `icon` prop | Not as children (for plain/icon-only toggles) | ✅ Yes |

### Modal ⚠️

| Change | Details | Codemod |
|--------|---------|---------|
| Old Modal deprecated | Moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` | ✅ Yes |
