## 6. Import Path Changes

### 6.1 Core Import Path Changes

| PF5 Import | PF6 Import | Notes |
|------------|------------|-------|
| `@patternfly/react-core` | `@patternfly/react-core` | Same, but many components changed |
| `@patternfly/react-core/next` (Modal) | `@patternfly/react-core` | Next Modal promoted |
| `@patternfly/react-core/next` (DualListSelector) | `@patternfly/react-core` | Next DualListSelector promoted |
| `@patternfly/react-core` (old Modal) | `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` | Old Modal deprecated |
| `@patternfly/react-core` (old DualListSelector) | `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` | Old DualListSelector deprecated |
| `@patternfly/react-core` (Chip) | `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` | Chip deprecated |
| `@patternfly/react-core` (DragDrop) | `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` | DragDrop deprecated |

### 6.2 Charts Import Changes ⚠️

| PF5 Import | PF6 Import |
|------------|------------|
| `import { Chart } from '@patternfly/react-charts'` | `import { Chart } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory'` |
| `import { ChartArea } from '@patternfly/react-charts'` | `import { ChartArea } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory'` |
| All `@patternfly/react-charts` imports | `@patternfly/react-charts/victory` |

### 6.3 Deprecated Components Removed from `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`

These were previously in the deprecated path and are now **fully removed**:
- `ApplicationLauncher` — Use custom menu pattern
- `ContextSelector` — Use custom menu pattern
- `Dropdown` (old) — Use current composable Dropdown
- `OptionsMenu` — Use composable Select
- `PageHeader` — Use Masthead + Toolbar
- `Select` (old) — Use current composable Select

### 6.4 Form Interface Rename

| PF5 | PF6 |
|-----|-----|
| `FormFiledGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` | `FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` (typo fix) |

