## 7. Removed Features & Deprecated Components

### 7.1 Fully Removed Components
- **ApplicationLauncher** (from deprecated) — use custom menu
- **ContextSelector** (from deprecated) — use custom menu
- **Old Dropdown** (from deprecated) — use composable Dropdown
- **OptionsMenu** (from deprecated) — use composable Select
- **PageHeader** (from deprecated) — use Masthead + Toolbar
- **Old Select** (from deprecated) — use composable Select
- **KebabToggle** — use MenuToggle with `variant="plain"`
- **EmptyStateHeader** — merged into EmptyState props
- **EmptyStateIcon** — merged into EmptyState `icon` prop

