## Quick Reference: Most Impactful Changes for Kuadrant Console Plugin

Based on the project hints, these are the highest-priority changes:

1. **✅ Text/TextContent → Content** — Already noted in project
2. **✅ PageSection variant** — Only "default"/"secondary" — Already noted
3. **✅ EmptyState refactoring** — Structure simplified — Already noted
4. **✅ Modal from deprecated** — Import path change — Already noted
5. **⚠️ Button icon prop** — Icons must use `icon` prop, not children
6. **⚠️ CSS variables** — All `--pf-v5-*` → `--pf-v6-*` and `--pf-global-*` → `--pf-t--global--*`
7. **⚠️ Class names** — All `.pf-v5-c-*` → `.pf-v6-c-*`
8. **⚠️ Charts** — Import from `@patternfly/react-charts/victory`
9. **⚠️ FormGroup labelIcon → labelHelp**
10. **⚠️ Nav variant="tertiary" → "horizontal-subnav"**
11. **⚠️ Tabs isSecondary → isSubtab**
12. **⚠️ Toolbar chip props → label props**
13. **⚠️ Chip → Label migration**
14. **⚠️ Dark theme** — Use `.pf-theme-dark` or `.pf-v6-theme-dark`

