    <ul>
      <li><code>SelectOption</code> children must be wrapped in <code>&lt;SelectList&gt;</code></li>
      <li>Selection callback types changed: <code>string</code> → <code>string | number | undefined</code></li>
      <li><code>popperProps={{ appendTo: 'inline' }}</code> recommended for proper positioning</li>
      <li>Disabled dropdown items use <code>tooltipProps</code> instead of wrapping with <code>&lt;Tooltip&gt;</code></li>
      <li><code>InputGroupItem</code> wrapper required for inputs inside <code>InputGroup</code></li>
    </ul>

