<!-- 6f. ToolbarFilter nesting -->
<details>
  <summary>🔧 ToolbarFilter / ToolbarItem Nesting &nbsp; <span class="badge badge-green">semver wins</span></summary>
  <div class="detail-body">
    <h4>What Changed in PF6</h4>
    <p>PF6 requires <code>&lt;ToolbarFilter&gt;</code> to be the <strong>parent</strong> of <code>&lt;ToolbarItem&gt;</code>, not the reverse.</p>

    <h4>Before (main — ResourceFilterToolbar.tsx)</h4>
<pre><code>&lt;ToolbarItem variant="label-group"&gt;
  &lt;ToolbarFilter categoryName="Resource" ...&gt;
    &lt;Select .../&gt;
  &lt;/ToolbarFilter&gt;
&lt;/ToolbarItem&gt;</code></pre>

    <h4>After — semver/goose</h4>
<pre><code>&lt;ToolbarFilter categoryName="Resource" ...&gt;
  &lt;ToolbarItem variant="label-group"&gt;
    &lt;Select .../&gt;
  &lt;/ToolbarItem&gt;
&lt;/ToolbarFilter&gt;</code></pre>

    <p><strong>pf-codemods:</strong> No change. <strong>semver:</strong> Correctly inverted nesting order + updated <code>handleSelect</code> type to <code>SelectOptionProps['value']</code>.</p>
  </div>
</details>

